text: Leen Korpershoek (29 January 1904 - 24 July 1989) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rotterdam Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
